      "title": "Longindying call",
      "color": "#CF2929",
      "tag": "The Body",
      "snippet": "And a call, pure, long and throbbing. Longindying call. / a call came, long in dying. That was a tuningfork the tuner had that he forgot that he now struck. A call again. That he now poised that it now throbbed. You hear? It throbbed, pure, purer, softly and softlier, its buzzing prongs. Longer in dying call.",
      "order": 7,
      "url": "https://www.joyceproject.com/notes/b7dZBJcB31HfjHCgc6JT"
    },
