      "title": "Ben Dollard",
      "color": "#307EE3",
      "tag": "The Writer",
      "snippet": "Big Benaben. Big Benben. / Ben Dollard&#x27;s vague bass / Ben Dollard&#x27;s voice. Base barreltone. Doing his level best to say it. Croak of vast manless moonless womoonless marsh. Other comedown. Big ships&#x27; chandler&#x27;s business he did once. Remember: rosiny ropes, ships&#x27; lanterns. Failed to the tune of ten thousand pounds. Now in the Iveagh home. Cubicle number so and so. Number one Bass did that for him.",
      "order": 17,
      "url": "https://www.joyceproject.com/notes/qk-bJZUBeQi-aLQfe7F3"
    },
